metadata.name: you list you lose #1/6
metadata.description:
Ain't it funny how I welcomed you into my family for free? You expected more free gifts? Well here is your first one. You had SIMS&CO. listed for sale, so this will be the only airdrop you EVER get. Congratulations on getting clownlisted.

Your token (SIMS&CO) and address is now clownlisted unless it is sold to someone, even if it's to yourself. Transfers, or a free sale does not count. This story does not come without consequences. I do not appreciate clowns. 

This token is worthless. Whoever owns it is banned from receiving my art forever. You can try transferring out but that will not help you. You were already snapshotted.

DO NOT BUY.
